{"word":"G2588 - καρδία - kardía - kar-dee'-ah - Heart","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καρδία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kardía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kar-dee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heart"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"இருதயம், மனம், உள்ளம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"the heart, soul, mind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Prolonged from a primary <b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C1;</b> <b>kar</b> (Latin <i>cor</i>, &ldquo;heart&rdquo;); the <i>heart</i>, that is, (figuratively) the <i>thoughts</i> or <i>feelings</i> (<i>mind</i>); also (by analogy) the <i>middle:</i> - (+ broken-) heart (-ed)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2588 - καρδία - kardía - kar-dee'-ah/2588\">G2588</a>, <a href=\"#/G2589 - καρδιογνώστης - kardiognṓstēs - kar-dee-og-noce'-tace/2589\">G2589</a>, <a href=\"#/G4641 - σκληροκαρδία - sklērokardía - sklay-rok-ar-dee'-ah/4641\">G4641</a>"}]}